            "failure_message": "Requires a spotlight-style lock-in: strong anxiety plus embarrassment/awkwardness, grounded in high threat, negative self-evaluation, and high engagement (hyper-self-monitoring) with somewhat reduced control. Caps anger to avoid defensiveness, and caps dissociation/numbness so it stays present and keyed-up. Triggers only when threat spikes alongside engagement staying high and rising (the spotlight 'clicks on')."
